Package: lgpr
Title: Longitudinal Gaussian Process Regression
Version: 0.29.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Juho",
           family = "Timonen",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "juho.timonen@aalto.fi",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2341-6765"))
Description: Implements interpretable nonparametric analysis and
             covariate selection for longitudinal data using additive
             Gaussian process regression. Includes specialized non-stationary disease
             effect modeling features for biomedical studies. Bayesian inference for
             model parameters is performed using Stan.
